data.description: Welcome to the Riverwalk – highly sought-after in the heart of Chesapeake! This vibrant neighborhood is just minutes away from major highways and shopping hotspots, offering the perfect blend of options and convenience. From the expansive clubhouse to the inviting in-ground pool, tennis courts, and scenic trails, and fountains there's always something exciting to explore right outside your door. With extra space off the primary bedroom that could be used as office space or to unwind – complete with a cozy fireplace – this home is designed for modern living at its finest. Enter inside to be greeted by another fireplace downstairs, complemented by a stunning staircase. The HVAC is practically new, ensuring comfort and peace of mind for years to come. Don't miss this one! Arrange a tour today.
